<p class="EnTeteTranscription">Wilcocke, Samuel Hull. Narrative of Circumstances attending the death of the late Benjamin Frobisher, Esquire a partner of the North West Company of Montreal, ca. 1820 <span class="AddHand-editors">[Revised Text]</span>. An electronic transcription. MFTP #0020</p><div class="ContenuPage">
